# MCP Configuration Template

## Overview
Model Context Protocol (MCP) configuration for Claude Code skills integration.

## Server Configuration
```yaml
server:
  name: {SKILL_NAME}
  version: "1.0.0"
  description: "{SKILL_DESCRIPTION}"
```

## Resources
```yaml
resources:
  - uri: "skill:///{SKILL_NAME}/config"
    name: "Configuration"
    mimeType: "application/json"
    
  - uri: "skill:///{SKILL_NAME}/state"
    name: "State"
    mimeType: "application/json"
```

## Tools
```yaml
tools:
  - name: {TOOL_NAME}
    description: "{TOOL_DESCRIPTION}"
    inputSchema:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        {PARAMETERS}
      required: [{REQUIRED_PARAMS}]
      
  - name: {TOOL_NAME_2}
    description: "{TOOL_DESCRIPTION_2}"
    inputSchema:
      type: "object"
      properties:
        {PARAMETERS_2}
      required: [{REQUIRED_PARAMS_2}]
```

## Prompts
```yaml
prompts:
  - name: "{PROMPT_NAME}"
    description: "{PROMPT_DESCRIPTION}"
    arguments:
      - name: "{ARGUMENT}"
        description: "{ARGUMENT_DESCRIPTION}"
```

## Environment Variables
```yaml
env:
  LOG_LEVEL: "info"
  DEBUG: "false"
  {CUSTOM_VAR}: "{CUSTOM_VALUE}"
```

## Capabilities
```yaml
capabilities:
  resources: true
  tools: true
  sampling: true
```

## Connection Settings
```yaml
transport:
  type: "stdio"  # or "sse", "ws"
```
